      "versionNonce": 623558371,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772552712122,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "this page will have a enter\nbutton which will take\nuser's to the core user\ninterface page",
      "fontSize": 54.39680778654761,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "this page will have a enter button which will take user's to the core user interface page",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "GBf9BWPpK6B5AtsJKlCBa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1582.5970122965573,
      "y": 8863.827444330322,
      "width": 789.0164500604486,
      "height": 405.8080189907922,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "as",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 524067363,
      "version": 304,
      "versionNonce": 1174573431,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772605227616,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "when clicked on the webapp it will\nask for google auth login or sign\nus as we have to incorporate\ndatabase to store the nodes and\nall texts and etc being done in\nthe canvas by different user's, so\nhave to incorporate google auth.",
      "fontSize": 46.3780593132334,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "when clicked on the webapp it will ask for google auth login or sign us as we have to incorporate database to store the nodes and all texts and etc being done in the canvas by different user's, so have to incorporate google auth.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Q0wEdx2q_Xq1H0-c-kZqL",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1556.7252986200965,
      "y": 10336.333802724894,
      "width": 1182.8150893850504,
      "height": 533.7647649273383,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "at",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1334930659,
      "version": 555,
      "versionNonce": 1907504147,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772796382147,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "So it will be the main user interface after\n1st and 2nd page and it will be the canvas\nwhere user's can dump and do everything\nwith colors, brushes, pens, pencils, fonts,\nlinks, highlights, adding image or video or\naudio. It's an infinite canvas but users can\nalso make multiple different infinite canvas\ninstances.",
      "fontSize": 53.376476492733815,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "So it will be the main user interface after 1st and 2nd page and it will be the canvas where user's can dump and do everything with colors, brushes, pens, pencils, fonts, links, highlights, adding image or video or audio. It's an infinite canvas but users can also make multiple different infinite canvas instances.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
