      "text": "Will have a floating ai sidebar it will be generally hidden upon clicked on button it\nwill be visible and hover above the infinite canvas, and why it will be used it to\nsummarize the whiteboard what's written there and etc, it can suggest fixes and\nall it will also consist image and voice support like if I click the voice option and\nsay zoom the canvas to this part it will do it and etc and can even highlight if I\nask it to do something it can do all it can even make a new canvas and write\ninside that with proper structure, and it can even generate architecture and\ndiagram based on summarized context (for now will generate and add outlines\nbased if possible will add generation of images and adding them to canvas)",
      "fontSize": 44.04621845789829,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Will have a floating ai sidebar it will be generally hidden upon clicked on button it will be visible and hover above the infinite canvas, and why it will be used it to summarize the whiteboard what's written there and etc, it can suggest fixes and all it will also consist image and voice support like if I click the voice option and say zoom the canvas to this part it will do it and etc and can even highlight if I ask it to do something it can do all it can even make a new canvas and write inside that with proper structure, and it can even generate architecture and diagram based on summarized context (for now will generate and add outlines based if possible will add generation of images and adding them to canvas)",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
